This paper discusses the statistical properties of directed networks and their ranking using PageRank and CheiRank algorithms. The focus is on analyzing information flow and developing two-dimensional search engines. This work is related to information retrieval (cs.IR), social networks (cs.SI), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), cybersecurity (cs.CY), and system and control (cs.SD).
